      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Crystal_River%2C_Florida"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "text": "Crystal River sits on the northeast side of Kings Bay, an inlet of the Gulf of Mexico that defines the heart of Florida’s Nature Coast.",
